	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro benevolentia vestra, pater reverende, quam mihi nuper exhibuistis, gratias vobis ago maximas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Die solis, cum iam advesperasceret domum veni; meos omnes salvos et incolumes offendi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In via ad <placeName type="citizen_name">Wesen</placeName> incidi in <persName ref="p3716" cert="high">Rodolphum a Salicibus</persName> capitaneum, hominem mirae modestiae, qui reliquum iter mihi comes fuit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is mihi in via, cum simul equis iremus, dixit se pro comperto habere pacem esse factam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc mihi ita probabat: se, antequam se viae daret, convenisse ducem <placeName type="auto_name">Ferrariensem</placeName> rogasseque, si quid de pace actum esset, sibi pro veteri erga se benevolentia impertiret.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ducem vero respondisse se iam meditari abitum; nisi autem pax facta esset, se missionem vix a rege impetraturum fuisse.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Dux Guisius</persName> ab eodem salutatus in eadem verba respondit: <persName type="citizen_name">Sabaudus</persName> ducat regis sororem; rex restituat <placeName type="citizen_name">Sabaudiam</placeName>, non <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemontem</placeName>, pro <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemonte</placeName> autem solvat francos octoginta mille annuos; <persName type="citizen_name"><placeName type="citizen_name">Sabaudus</placeName></persName> sit feudarius regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliae</placeName>; restituat etiam rex <placeName type="citizen_name">Sabaudo</placeName> comitatum <placeName type="citizen_name">Burgobrässensem</placeName>; loca munita uterque rex sibi mutuo restituant uno <placeName type="citizen_name">Caleto</placeName> excepto; mortem reginae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliae</placeName> magnum momentum ad hanc pacem attulisse.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">An vero sponsalia futura sint inter <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> filium et regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallorum</placeName> filiam, de eo adhuc dubitatur; connestablius in eo multum laborare fertur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der kunig uß <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franckrych</placeName> bütet des <persName type="citizen_name">Philippi</persName> sun syn dochter an mit dem geding, das er syn anspraach, so er vermeint ze han an das herzogthumb <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Meyland</placeName> übergebe, des glychen auch <persName type="citizen_name">Philippus</persName> thuͦn sölle, und sölle also das herzogthuͦm des <persName type="citizen_name">Philippi</persName> sun zuͦgestelt werden; wyter sölle <persName type="citizen_name">Philippus</persName> synem sun das künigrych <placeName ref="l994" cert="high">Neapolis</placeName> übergeben.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Philippus</persName> aber wendet für, wie er andere kinder überkommen möchte, die er nit so gar könne berouben etc.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec capitaneus, quae ego quidem, ut audivi, scribo, certi nihil affirmo; tu haec boni nunc consulas.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, reverende pater, et omnibus bonis viris ex me salutem dicito.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Collino</persName> etiam socero significabis, iter satis feliciter successisse, apud nos praeterea omnia esse salva.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale iterum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiae</placeName> 12. decembris anno 1558.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Iohannes Fabricius</persName> tui observantissimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro eruditione et pietate excellenti d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tigurinae antistiti fidelissimo, domino et patrono suo multum observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
